by your success.

288
00:23:43,980 --> 00:23:46,580
What we need now is a muscular Christian.

289
00:23:47,100 --> 00:23:49,980
To make folks sit up and notice.

290
00:23:50,060 --> 00:23:52,500
How good are you, Eric?

291
00:23:53,260 --> 00:23:56,820
