444
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:49,920
I'd heard you were both the best.

445
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:52,080
And what do you think now?

446
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:54,240
Eric Liddell?

447
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:58,000
